Confluent Theorists who produced the Convergence Codices documented several interaction effects
that Rivennid practitioners already intuitively understood from their network-mediated perception.
Rivennid who study Circle-lineage arcane tradition report that the Confluence Texts feel like
external documentation of things they already knew from the inside.

