material transformation orientation in ways the Axiomatic Schools' bounded-domain formalism
does not. The Cinderteeth's volcanic processes are multi-school interaction effects at geological
scale. Ashborn who have studied both traditions consistently report that Circle methodology
describes their embodied experience more accurately.
